<ab facs="#facs_473_r2l20">~ der <expan>kurfürſte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd des tags <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>Regenſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> oder bey vns etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_473_r2l21">das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd als vıl wır noch <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_473_r2l22">ſo hat der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der <expan>R<ex>ömiſch</ex></expan> künıg <expan>ſölıche<ex>n</ex></expan> tag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_473_r2l23">gen <expan>Regenſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> geſecʒt vnd wır <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> daʒ ʒu <expan>Regenſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_473_r2l24">ʒu Paſſaw dıe gemein red ſey . daʒ ſeın <expan>künıgl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade kurcʒlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_473_r2l25"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>auf</expan> ʒu lande <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſülle vnd daʒ man ſıch auch ʒu <expan>Regenſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_474" id="236r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_474_r1l1">mıt <expan>herberge<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſölıche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>dınge<ex>n</ex></expan> vaſt darcʒu gerıcht habe . So </ab>
