<ab facs="#facs_474_line_1592198069740_186"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
